query:
SELECT DISTINCT
                o.id,
                o.name,
                o.created_at,
                o.updated_at
            FROM organizations o
            INNER JOIN user_organizations uo ON uo.organization_id = o.id
            WHERE uo.user_id = $1
            AND o.created_at < (
                SELECT created_at FROM organizations WHERE id = $2
            )
            ORDER BY o.created_at DESC
            LIMIT $3
